html:
CacheDataType.Partial

Stores only a portion of data in the cache. It is used to load data collection.

CacheDataType.Full

Stores the data in the cache entirely. It is used to load a single record. When you use the CacheDataType.Full parameter value, make sure that all required columns are set to the attributes parameter.
